uling'),(1301,99,'wpcf-service-list-item','Project Coordination & Setup'),(1302,101,'wpcf-service-name','Build'),(1303,101,'wpcf-service-description','Red Wave Communications ensures the utmost professionalism when providing our services while incorporating the most efficient and latest technology, industry standard practices, project analysis, project management, and cost effective, timely results.'),(1304,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Pre-construction Services'),(1305,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Engineering & Job Analysis'),(1306,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Budget & Estimating'),(1307,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Scheduling'),(1308,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Job site Coordination'),(1309,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Finalizing Job Completion'),(1310,103,'wpcf-service-name','Maintain'),(1311,103,'wpcf-service-description','Red Wave Communications’ service department maintains, tests, and inspects a wide range of facilities in California. We support everything from small, family-owned restaurants to enterprise corporations like regional hospitals. We offer the most experienced and efficient technicians who are provided with the latest tools and technology to improve the identification and repair of nearly all types of communications, safety, and low voltage systems in secured and unsecured buildings.'),(1312,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Two hour response time'),(1313,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','24/7 service 365 days a year'),(1314,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Diagnosis and repair of fire panels, sound equipment, cameras, AV, data, access control systems, video surveillance, automation, and more.'),(1315,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','System Network Integration'),(1316,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Inspection Compliance Reporting by BuildingReports'),(1317,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Test & inspect'),(1318,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Remote service capabilities'),(1319,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Offsite data management'),(1344,71,'_wp_old_slug','audio-video'),(1363,80,'wpcf-system-name','Business Automation'),(1364,80,'wpcf-system-description','With automation, the possibilities are endless. Red Wave Communications partners with some of today’s leading manufacturers and designers to get the solution you need. We can design an all purpose control for your business that incorporates lighting, sound, music, networking, video, security, temperature control, cameras, gate control, and more.'),(1365,80,'wpcf-system-list','Control4'),(1366,80,'wpcf-system-list','Crestron'),(1367,80,'wpcf-system-list','Extron Electronics'),(1372,82,'wpcf-system-name','Master Clock and PA Systems'),(1373,82,'wpcf-system-description','Red Wave Communications has partnered with Sapling who features a complete line of digital clock products for systems such as Wired, IP, TalkBack, and the synchronized wireless clock system which is based upon their patented frequency-hopping technology that has transformed the industry. We meticulously design sound and communications technologies to perform flawlessly on their own, efficiently with one another, and communicate with third party systems.'),(1374,82,'wpcf-system-list','Sapling'),(1375,82,'wpcf-system-list','Telecor'),(1376,84,'wpcf-system-name','Nurse Call'),(1377,84,'wpcf-system-description','To meet the growing demands of the healthcare industry, we offer top of the line nurse call systems providing both effective communication solutions and simple to use equipment.'),(1378,84,'wpcf-system-list','Jeron'),(1406,151,'wpcf-link','residential/#accordionPro214-slide-3'),(1407,150,'wpcf-link','residential/#accordionPro214-slide-4'),(1427,152,'wpcf-link','/residential/#accordionPro214-slide-2'),(1429,158,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-2'),(1430,157,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-3'),(1431,156,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-4'),(1432,154,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-5'),(1433,132,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-6'),(1434,155,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-7'),(1437,236,'_wp_attached_file','2015/02/red-square.png'),(1438,236,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:20;s:6:\"height\";i:20;s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"2015/02/red-square.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:0:{}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(1441,153,'wpcf-link','/business/#accordionPro213-slide-1'),(1444,4,'wpcf-about-certifications','<a href=\"http://pd.dgs.ca.gov/smbus/\"><strong>Small Business</strong></a>\r\n<em>This certification promotes California’s small business, and encourages sustained economic prosperity through working together to maintain the strength of small businesses throughout California.</em>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nicet.org/\"><strong>NICET</strong></a>\r\n<em>The National Institute for Certification in Engineering Technologies was created by the National Society of Professional Engineers to serve the certification needs of the engineering technology community.</em>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://bicsi.org/\"><strong>BICSI</strong></a>\r\n<em>The Building Industry Consulting Service International is a credential and assurance that an individual has knowledge in a designated area of information technology, systems design, or installation.</em>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://bicsi.org/rcdd\"><strong>RCDD</strong></a>\r\n<em>Registered Communications Distribution Designer demonstrated their knowledge in the design, implementation and integration of information technology, and related infrastructure.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>NFPA</strong>\r\n<em>National Fire Protection Association provides codes, standards, research, training, and education for all of its members in public safety and fire safety.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>BSIS</strong>\r\n<em>Bureau of Security and Investigated Service registers certified, professional security guards in the state of California.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>BBB</strong>\r\n<em>Accredited by the Better Business Bureau, which means we make a good faith effort to resolve any consumer complaints.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>CEDIA</strong>\r\n<em>Member of the Custom Electronic Design &amp; Installation Association.</em>'),(1445,4,'wpcf-about-company','Founded in 2002, Red Wave Communications Inc. has grown into a leading low voltage contractor throughout California, offering more than 30 years of combined experience and expertise in integration. Red Wave Communications is licensed by the California Contractors State License Board with A, B, C-7, and C-10 classifications. In addition, we are a State of California SBE organization, certified by the Department of General Services.'),(1446,94,'wpcf-system-name','Structured Cabling'),(1447,94,'wpcf-system-description','Red Wave Communications has partnered with some of the most elite manufactures to offer your facility a complete end-to-end solution for any environment.'),(1448,94,'wpcf-system-list','Berktek'),(1449,94,'wpcf-system-list','Commscope/Systimax'),(1450,94,'wpcf-system-list','Tyco'),(1457,66,'wpcf-system-name','Video Surveillance'),(1458,66,'wpcf-system-description','Red Wave Communications partners with leading manufacturers to provide you with the latest video surveillance technology in the industry. Whether you’re looking for a network camera, cost effective cameras, or high-speed dome cameras with positioning systems, we can provide for your everyday video surveillance needs.'),(1459,66,'wpcf-system-list','Avigilon'),(1460,66,'wpcf-system-list','Axis Communications'),(1461,66,'wpcf-system-list','Hikvision'),(1462,66,'wpcf-system-list','Lilin'),(1463,66,'wpcf-system-list','Vicon'),(1464,68,'wpcf-system-name','Fire Alarm'),(1465,68,'wpcf-system-description','Partnered with the best in the business, we install and service all your fire alarm needs whether in your retail space, office building, or government locations.'),(1466,68,'wpcf-system-list','EST'),(1467,68,'wpcf-system-list','Potter Signal'),(1468,71,'wpcf-system-name','Audiovisual'),(1469,71,'wpcf-system-description','From a simple smart board to a fully designed and built-out high tech conference room, we offer the highest quality when it comes to audiovisual solutions. We partner with incredible companies to bring these products to your business.'),(1470,71,'wpcf-system-list','BenQ'),(1471,71,'wpcf-system-list','BSS'),(1472,71,'wpcf-system-list','Crown'),(1473,71,'wpcf-system-list','EAW'),(1474,71,'wpcf-system-list','Egan Teamboard'),(1475,71,'wpcf-system-list','Electro-Voice'),(1476,71,'wpcf-system-list','Extron Electronics'),(1477,71,'wpcf-system-list','Frontrow'),(1478,71,'wpcf-system-list','JVC'),(1479,71,'wpcf-system-list','JBL'),(1480,71,'wpcf-system-list','Lab Gruppen'),(1481,71,'wpcf-system-list','QSC'),(1482,71,'wpcf-system-list','Rane'),(1483,71,'wpcf-system-list','Screen Innovations'),(1484,71,'wpcf-system-list','Sonance'),(1485,71,'wpcf-system-list','Tannoy'),(1486,90,'wpcf-system-name','Security Systems & Cameras'),(1487,90,'wpcf-system-description','Through the latest innovations in digital products, Red Wave Communications proudly protects your business with state of the art security monitoring.'),(1488,90,'wpcf-system-list','DMP: Digital Monitoring Products'),(1489,90,'wpcf-system-list','GE'),(1490,90,'wpcf-system-list','Videofied'),(1491,237,'_edit_lock','1429137299:1'),(1492,238,'_wp_attached_file','2015/04/home_automation.png'),(1493,238,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:203;s:6:\"height\";i:158;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2015/04/home_automation.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"home_automation-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:5:\"small\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:26:\"home_automation-120x93.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:120;s:6:\"height\";i:93;s:9:\"mim