rol'),(1512,53,'wpcf-system-description','Red Wave Communications offers some of the most technologically advanced equipment to keep your property safe. We can seamlessly integrate door control, alarm monitoring, enrollment, badging, video, intelligent graphics, reports, and database management.'),(1513,53,'wpcf-system-list','Brivo'),(1514,53,'wpcf-system-list','DSX Access System, Inc.'),(1515,53,'wpcf-system-list','Indentive Group formerly known as Hirsch Electronics'),(1516,53,'wpcf-system-list','Paxton Access');
